@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableProjectName = complete_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableEmployeeProjectName = complete_employee_personal_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@projectWithUnfinishedNodesId = 5
@completedProjectId = 3
@missingProjectId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0

### 提示：正常路径和部分异常路径会先创建临时项目，因此可以重复回放

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建可手动完成的临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证手动完成项目接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2099-12-31"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableCompleteProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员手动完成刚创建的临时项目，预期 status=3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableCompleteProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录手动完成项目，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectWithUnfinishedNodesId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：普通员工创建个人自用临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableEmployeeProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证管理员不能代完成普通员工个人项目。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2099-12-31"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableEmployeeCompleteProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：管理员不能手动完成普通员工创建的个人自用项目，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableEmployeeCompleteProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工手动完成非本人负责项目，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectWithUnfinishedNodesId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：项目下存在未完成阶段节点，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectWithUnfinishedNodesId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：已完成项目不能重复完成，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{completedProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectWithUnfinishedNodesId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}
